MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Ω God, right?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I don't know who you are, what your ideology is, or what your purpose is in your actions. I don't care, I'm neither interested, nor do I want to understand.
Her gun in hand, countless penguins lined up around Asahikawa. They dexterously manoeuvred heavy weapons with their wings, waiting for their Queen to issue orders.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Who cares, just die because you are in my way. Just die because you are my enemy. Anyone identified as my enemy by the so kawaii me should go to Hell, no questions asked.
Asahikawa raised her hand in the air while reiterating her typical selfish mindset.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Your wishes, your hopes, everything.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: -- They'll all be encased in ice.

At that moment, Asahikawa lowered her hand and simultaneously fired her gun wildly. The penguins around her began firing in unison, with the familiar aura of mercenaries who have fought many battles in the past.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I'll freeze you, admire wherever you're worth liking, then shatter you into pieces, and throw them away on my whims.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That's what you want, no? That's what you were born for.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'GAAAAAAAH!?'

The gigantic Ω God screamed in agony as it is shot all over its body. While its ability to brainwash people and force them to love each other is troublesome, it itself does not seem to be that tough physically.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Hmph. You're fragile and weak, yet you're foolish enough to reveal yourself and propagate your own ideology, utter idiocy.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Small fry should be self-aware that they're small fry and just hide in the dark, like failures you are.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'NO! NEVER AGAIN! NOOOO--!'
Ω God goes berserk, wielding tentacles all over its body. Each time it did this, buildings were smashed to pieces and the inhabitants of Sheep City screamed and fled.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Woah, it's like Naraka.
Asahikawa, stop trying to over-agitate the enemy. Also, you can't just start attacking on your own. Allow innocent civilians to properly evacuate first, wait for my instructions and then--

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Silence. Nobody gives me orders.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I am the ruler of Doubutsuen, the greatest Ice Queen in the world. I was born to be, and I was wanted to be.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: THAT IS MY FATE! FROM THE DAY I WAS BORN, UNTIL NOW!
Asahikawa yelled furiously and continued to fire bullets wildly. Khajuraho looked at her with amusement and smiled as she whipped away incoming debris.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Haha, great expressions♪ You could make a face like that too huh, when your face was usually so unfathomable that I wouldn't know what you're thinking!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Great, I'm getting aroused myself... I sure want to crack my whip and break everything that girl is trying so hard to protect into a mess♪
Khajuraho, I don't want to repeat myself again, don't do anything to hurt your own people. If they've given their consent, then it's up to them, and I won't interfere in that case.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: ...Yeah. I understand. For I'm a pro, I offer services upon demand.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That's what I'm proud of, as a tamer.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I'm sorry, but the quavers that Ω God is emitting from its whole body are making it hard for me to hold back my 'expressions of love'.
Is that why Asahikawa seems to be somewhat upset?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Probably. because of Ω God's influence, everyone's affected. Sooner or later, we might not be able to think about anything else and just follow Ω God's ideology - and be only homosexual.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Gaugh～, gaugh～...♪ Jeran, your tail is so cute - can you tangle yours with Yours Truly's? Can we make love, tail to tail?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: No problem dah～ Sentosa, do what you want! Hyan, so ticklish dah～♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: ...Just like that. I wish I could make love to someone without thinking about it.
If we don't take down Ω God soon, it's going to be a repeat of last year's Valentine's Day. I almost developed gynophobia because of that, and I don't want the same thing to happen again.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Ah, something like a love potion was popular last year, wasn't it?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That's why the girls in the SSS were pushing Bro down and had themselves rub you around - Ah, a pity that I haven't got myself enlisted last year♪
Khajuraho licked her lips bewitchingly and walked over to me.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That's the thing, we should really defeat Ω God as soon as possible. If only everyone loved each other, it would be an ideal paradise for me too.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: But Ω God instils hostility towards the opposite sex along with love for the same sex. You're not influenced by it right now because Asahi and I are protecting Bro with spells and other powers and stuff, but...

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Sooner or later, you will be swallowed up by the worldview that Ω God has built up. Then Bro will start to hate the opposite sex - Us.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That's what Asahi is afraid of. She is a spoilt child who wants to be loved and is extremely averse to losing your favour, Bro.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Of course. It would be bad if all of us if you, our commander, starts to dislike us.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You don't want to talk to someone you don't like and you would not care of their fates. If that happens, the chain of command and everything else will collapse - We will be wiped out for sure.
I don't hate any of you. You're all 'difficult to deal with' in the eyes of the public, but that's precisely what I appreciate and love about all of you.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Thanks. But you should tell that kind of thing to the other kids aside myself.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I am a trained priestess, I can reassure myself. I know how to put myself in a good mood and I can do my job even without love.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: However, others aren't like that. They're always insecure and shaky, desperate not to be disliked, and desperate for someone to affirm them.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: It's your role to reassure these girls, 'Conductor'.
Khajuraho unusually addressed me with the 'Conductor' title, tiptoed a little and kissed me on the cheek.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That's settled, then. Once again, I've carefully protected you. It should keep you sane for a while, preventing Ω God's quaver effects.
Thank you. And while you're at it, bring Jeran and Sentosa back to their senses. It's going to be difficult for Asahikawa and her penguins to defeat the Ω God in time.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yeah. Let's have the rampage-loving kids do their best.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'Let's all work together and do our best' is the orders I got from you.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I'll follow your orders, because I'm a member of the SSS too.
Saying this, Khajuraho dashingly held up her whip.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Now, come to your senses! Move on! I'll whip you up if you don't do what I say, come, come, come♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: WAAAAAAAAH!? OW OW OW OW! Stop whipping me! What are you doing all of a sudden, siao ah--!?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Wha wha wha what's going on dah～? Why does Khajuraho always do such terrible things dah～!?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Huh, I wonder why? Maybe its because I don't like you girls?
I already knew that what she said just now was a blatant lie.
